<item>
            <title>[PIG-2257] AvroStorage doesn&apos;t recognize schema_file field when JSON isn&apos;t used in the constructor</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-2257</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-2195&quot; title=&quot;AvroStorage fails to STORE when LOADing via PigStorage&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PIG-2195&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PIG-2195&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; introduced the &lt;tt&gt;schema_file&lt;/tt&gt; constructor param to &lt;tt&gt;AvroStorage&lt;/tt&gt;. This field is currently only supported when passing constructor data via JSON though (a different code path is used when constructor data is a String array).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12520856">PIG-2257</key>
            <summary>AvroStorage doesn&apos;t recognize schema_file field when JSON isn&apos;t used in the constructor</summary>
