                            <comment id="13239955" author="dvryaboy" created="Tue, 27 Mar 2012 22:09:44 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Whoa, ancient times. Peeps who work with Avro, do you need this?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13240117" author="billgraham" created="Wed, 28 Mar 2012 03:25:33 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;This is actually a bug that should be patched. All constructs to &lt;tt&gt;AvroStorage&lt;/tt&gt; should work whether being passed as json or a string array, but &lt;tt&gt;schema_file&lt;/tt&gt; was only implemented in the former.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
